				<a class='comment-reply-link' href='/2012/05/24/15327-ne-lappelez-plus-jamais-eurobonds?replytocom=74233#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm("comment-74233", "74233", "respond", "15327")'>Répondre</a>							</div>
